sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant API as Flask API (/api/v1/ask)
    participant QAS as QAService
    participant RAG as RAGWorkflow
    participant SE as SearchEngine
    participant LLM as Ollama LLM
    
    U->>FE: types query & clicks "Analyze"
    FE->>API: POST { query, use_llm: true }
    API->>QAS: answer_query(query, useLLM=true)
    QAS->>RAG: ask(query, retrieve_only=False)
    RAG->>SE: search(query, top_k=5)
    SE-->>RAG: ranked article list
    RAG->>SE: check_model_availability()
    SE-->>RAG: model available
    RAG->>LLM: chat(prompt with article context)
    LLM-->>RAG: generated answer
    RAG-->>QAS: {answer, retrieved_articles}
    QAS-->>API: payload with response
    API-->>FE: JSON response
    FE-->>U: displays answer & articles


